{"id":299628,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-长沙维权人士刘华在看守所中患肾结石，/","date":"2013-06-18T13:34:27Z","modified":"2013-06-18T13:34:27Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙维权人士刘华在看守所中患肾结石，律师请求取保候审（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span></span></span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span></span>6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日上午，长沙维权人士刘华从长沙市第一看守所给妈妈打电话，他在监狱里发病得了肾结石，痛得厉害已经有二天了，亟需救治！刘华在电话中喊“妈妈救我”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日，刘华的辩护律师刘建民向长沙市公安局芙蓉分局发函，因刘华患肾结石，请求为其申请取保候审。同日，刘华妈妈哭着去找了湖南省检察院控申处处长段志凌，希望检察院救救刘华。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月，刘华、李颂明、曾武、邓生记等人因前往迎接从北京被押回的访民遭逮捕，罪名是危害公共安全，期间不断遭遇延长审查起诉期限，一直关押在长沙市第一看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HIBXsIGCRQM/UcAgoQZ5xSI/AAAAAAAAjnQ/1XG9ZYTeK-Y/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HIBXsIGCRQM/UcAgoQZ5xSI/AAAAAAAAjnQ/1XG9ZYTeK-Y/s320/1.JPG\" width=\"215\" /></a></div>\n<p> </p></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],